  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to assess the effect of spinal anaesthesia against a general anaesthesia with
      a femoral block, with respect to the incidence of chronic pain following a total knee
      replacement.

      It will also focus on genetic factors and their influence on chronic pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
